Executive Profile
Michael D. Shmerling CPAManaging Partner, XMi High Growth Development Fund, LLCAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 9 Board Members in 9 different organizations across 9 different industries.See Board Relationships61--
Background

		Mr. Michael D. Shmerling, also known as Mike, CPA, has been an Executive Vice President of Kroll, Inc. since September 20, 2001. Mr. Shmerling serves as a Managing Partner of XMi High Growth Development Fund, LLC. He served as the Chief Executive Officer at XMi Holdings, Inc. He began his career in 1977 at Ernst & Ernst. He founded companies include Transcor America Inc., Corrections Partners, Inc., Amicus Legal Staffing and Background America, Inc. He served as the ... Chief Operating Officer of Kroll Risk Consulting Services, Inc. since August 2000. He serves as the Chairman of the Board at XMi Holdings, Inc., LocalShares, Inc. and Choice Food Group, Inc. He has been Vice Chairman of Nashville Area Chamber of Commerce since July 3, 2014. He has been a Director of Kroll, Inc. since August 2001. He has been an Independent Director of Renasant Corp. since July 1, 2007. He has been a Director of HealthStream, Inc. since November 2005. He is the Founder of the Nashville Entrepreneur Center and serves on the Boards of Directors of Community Foundation of Middle Tennessee, Nashville Area Chamber Of Commerce, United Way of Metropolitan Nashville, Monroe Carrell Vanderbilt Children’s Hospital and The Hermitage. He serves as a Director at Crescent Banking Company. He was a Charter Shareholder and a Board Member of Tennessee-based Capital Bank and Trust and he continues to serves on the Board of Renasant Bank, N.A. He served as an Independent Director of Capital Bancorp Inc. since 2001. He served as Director of Capital Bank & Trust Company since 1997. He served as a Director of Consensus Point, Inc. He served on the Boards of Fisk University, Tennessee Performing Arts Center, Nashville Public Library Foundation and Tennessee Society of CPAs. Mr. Shmerling holds the Certified Public Accountant designation. He received a Bachelor of Accountancy degree from the University of Oklahoma in 1977.Read Full Background




